{
  "stem": "18486.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 478.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it had a lid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- and we had made a double bottom in it, so that you could get in from the house through a wall, which you'd move.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they could all go in as they did it one after the other, because it would end up in the reservation [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you could only get into the false wall through the studio.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only through the coal bin, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had meeting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, oh, you mean--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there-- no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there came--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our friends came to our house, and they didn't know what we were doing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some did, who [INAUDIBLE] in our own group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had razias, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We called it razias.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--when you got an-- how you say that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A raid.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A raid is an razia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they would come to your door, and when you opened, they put your-- their foot in already that you couldn't close it again and they came in and they searched your house.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They've never found one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two are caught, who tried to escape to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was a young married couple.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they couldn't stand being locked up and hidden.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- they-- they-- you know, they rebel too much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said, we are going to try to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were caught at-- at the frontier and shot, both.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But all the others survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not when they didn't have any paper which showed me from which group they came or from which people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once there came a man who was very obviously Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no doubt about for me that he was a Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but he had no paper and nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
